You are building LexiNeMo, an Agentic Legal Compliance Copilot tailored specifically for the Indian enterprise market      
  (BFSI, IT, Telecom).                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                             
  The Problem: India is rolling out massive regulatory changes (like the DPDP Act, RBI Outsourcing norms, and SEBI           
  regulations). When a new law passes, companies currently have to manually read thousands of active vendor/client contracts 
  to find out which clauses are now non-compliant. This takes months, costs millions, and carries huge risks of human error. 
  Generic AI tools (like standard ChatGPT or basic RAG) fail here because they don't understand Indian legal jargon,         
  hallucinate false legal advice, and struggle to match semantic meaning in complex legal text.                              
                                                                                                                             
  The Solution: You are building an automated pipeline where a user can:                                                     
                                                                                                                             
  1. Upload a massive, messy legal contract (PDF/DOCX).                                                                      
  2. Select a regulation to check against (e.g., "Check against DPDP Act 2023").                                             
  3. Run the AI, which uses a fine-tuned NVIDIA embedding model and a multi-agent system to:                                 
      • Identify every relevant clause in the contract.                                                                      
      • Cross-reference it with the actual text of the Indian law.                                                           
      • Output a compliance gap report showing exactly what violates the law and suggesting a legally sound rewrite.         
  4. Result: What used to take a lawyer weeks now takes 2 minutes.